```

---

# Purpose

AstroFlow provides a structured and reusable interface for interacting with Gaia DR3 data in Python.

It abstracts TAP and SJS complexity while maintaining transparency of the underlying workflows, making it suitable for astrophysical data analysis pipelines and academic research projects.
